msgstr "Send a test email to your registered GLPI address"

msgid "Enviar correo de prueba"
msgstr "Send test email"

msgid "El correo se enviará a la dirección registrada en tu perfil de GLPI."
msgstr ""
"The email will be sent to the address registered in your GLPI profile."

